{"tid":1449073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:17:34.000Z","uid":220764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f374bfd31aa193b90ad5c42145e116cae9a112a8","tid":1449073,"uid":220764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:29.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=5271cbd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=894a269c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"d675d9ff8fee88c66777c56d3eb984a97126343b","tid":1449073,"uid":9192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f443870480950c1239551f1812cd4f43065ca31","tid":1449073,"uid":220764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"就算唔罷工，放左工都入黎機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你地！！"},{"pid":"d2b170d2e6e6f9a79a1630665d8fccc260cd3411","tid":1449073,"uid":220764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3f88223a3356558624c7c6b51